  "name": "Wilzen \"Cuco\" Pérez",
  "body_es": "<div class=\"section-featured is-featured-image\">\n\t<div class=\"featured-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0133edit.jpg)\"></div>\n\t<div class=\"featured-wrap flex\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"featured-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"tags-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"post-tag global-tag\" href=\"/tag/artesanos/\">Artesanos</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"post-tag global-tag\" href=\"/tag/madera/\">Madera</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"post-tag global-tag\" href=\"/tag/imagineria/\">Imaginería</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"post-tag global-tag\" href=\"/tag/estampa-tipica/\">Estampa Típica</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"white\">Wilzen &quot;Cuco&quot; Pérez, Los Tres Reyes Magos en Carretas</h1>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-meta white\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>El folklore puertorriqueño en tus manos</span>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\t<div class=\"section-post wrap\">\n\t\t<div class=\"post-wrap \">\n\t\t\t<h3 id=\"documental-22\">Documental #22</h3><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2025/01/DSC_0122edit.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2025/01/DSC_0122edit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2025/01/DSC_0122edit.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2025/01/DSC_0122edit.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2025/01/DSC_0122edit.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>Conoce a Wilzen “Cuco” Pérez, artesano de Guánica dedicado a la creación de Los Tres Reyes en carretas. Su trabajo reúne tallado, memoria e imaginario puertorriqueño en piezas artesanales profundamente ligadas a nuestra cultura.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card kg-card-hascaption\"><figcaption><p><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Duración: 10 minutos 🎬 | Recomendamos ver nuestros documentales con el teléfono en posición horizontal o, mejor aún, en familia desde tu \"smart TV\". Para esto último, búscanos como </span><b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Obras del País</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> en el app de YouTube y </span><b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">suscríbete</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> 📺. Asegúrate de que la </span><b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">calidad del video esté en 1080p ⚙️.</strong></b></p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-toggle-card\" data-kg-toggle-state=\"close\">\n            <div class=\"kg-toggle-heading\">\n                <h4 class=\"kg-toggle-heading-text\"><b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Aviso de derechos de autor</strong></b></h4>\n                <button class=\"kg-toggle-card-icon\" aria-label=\"Expand toggle to read content\">\n                    <svg id=\"Regular\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                        <path class=\"cls-1\" d=\"M23.25,7.311,12.53,18.03a.749.749,0,0,1-1.06,0L.75,7.311\"></path>\n                    </svg>\n                </button>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"kg-toggle-content\"><p><br><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Todo el contenido publicado por </span><i><em class=\"italic\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Obras del País</em></i><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> —incluyendo videos, audios, imágenes, textos y materiales gráficos— está protegido por derechos de autor.</span></p><p><b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Agradecemos y fomentamos que compartas nuestro contenido utilizando los enlaces oficiales de nuestra página web y redes sociales.</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Eso nos ayuda a seguir difundiendo las historias que documentamos con tanto esmero.</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Sin embargo, </span><b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">no está permitido descargar, copiar, modificar ni volver a publicar nuestro contenido en otras plataformas sin autorización previa y sin el debido crédito.</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> El uso no autorizado afecta directamente el trabajo que realizamos junto a comunidades y artesanos en todo Puerto Rico.</span><br><br><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Para más información sobre el uso adecuado de nuestro material, acceda </span><a href=\"https://www.obrasdelpais.com/preguntas-frecuentes/\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">aquí</span></a><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Si deseas colaborar o compartir de otra manera, </span><a href=\"https://www.obrasdelpais.com/contactanos/\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">contáctanos</span></a><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">. Estamos abiertos a alianzas que respeten y amplifiquen esta labor.</span></p></div>\n        </div><h2 id=\"informaci%C3%B3n-de-contacto-del-artesano\">Información de contacto del artesano:</h2><h3 id=\"wilzen-cuco-p%C3%A9rez\"><br>Wilzen \"Cuco\" Pérez</h3><p><strong>🇵🇷 </strong>Municipio: Guánica<br>📞 787-821-2442  |  787-856-1469<br>📧  cucowilzen29@gmail.com<br>👥 Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100064041060480\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Wilzen \"Cuco\" Perez</a><br><br>💲 Tiene piezas comenzando desde $75 hasta piezas de más de $500. Todo depende del tamaño y la complejidad de la pieza.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-file-card\"><a class=\"kg-file-card-container\" href=\"https://www.obrasdelpais.com/content/files/2023/08/Wilzen-Cuco-Perez.png\" title=\"Download\" download=\"\"><div class=\"kg-file-card-contents\"><div class=\"kg-file-card-title\">Wilzen \"Cuco\" Perez</div><div class=\"kg-file-card-caption\">Descarga el QR Code de este perfil.</div><div class=\"kg-file-card-metadata\"><div class=\"kg-file-card-filename\">Wilzen Cuco Perez.png</div><div class=\"kg-file-card-filesize\">6 KB</div></div></div><div class=\"kg-file-card-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><defs><style>.a{fill:none;stroke:currentColor;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5px;}</style></defs><title>download-circle</title><polyline class=\"a\" points=\"8.25 14.25 12 18 15.75 14.25\"></polyline><line class=\"a\" x1=\"12\" y1=\"6.75\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"18\"></line><circle class=\"a\" cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11.25\"></circle></svg></div></a></div><p><strong>NOTA</strong>: <em>Obras del País no está vendiendo artesanías. Para conseguir piezas, comuníquese directamente con el artesano. </em>Cuando busques algo que regalar en un día especial, ¡piensa en un artesano boricua! ¡<strong>Y no olvides decirle que le conociste a través de Obras del País! </strong>🤗</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-callout-card kg-callout-card-yellow\"><div class=\"kg-callout-emoji\">✉️</div><div class=\"kg-callout-text\"><b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">¡No te pierdas nuestras publicaciones!</strong></b><br>Suscríbete y entérate de nuevos estrenos, de lo que pasa en la comunidad artesanal y acompáñanos en este camino hacia documentar a 100 artesanos boricuas.</div></div><hr><blockquote>\"La artesanía es importante que se siga preservando porque esa es la identidad de un pueblo. Un pueblo que no tiene cultura desaparece\".<br><br>- Wilzen \"Cuco\" Pérez</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0171edit.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/DSC_0171edit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/DSC_0171edit.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/07/DSC_0171edit.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0171edit.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h3 id=\"las-carretas-de-cuco\">Las carretas de Cuco</h3><p>Wilzen Pérez es el creador de los icónicos <strong>Reyes en carretas</strong> y nos llena de orgullo ver todos los elementos puertorriqueños que ha logrado incorporar a su artesanía. Para comenzar, Cuco recrea <strong>carretas puertorriqueñas</strong> que recorrían el archipiélago en épocas pasadas. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0282edit.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/DSC_0282edit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/DSC_0282edit.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/07/DSC_0282edit.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/07/DSC_0282edit.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0155edit.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/DSC_0155edit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/DSC_0155edit.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/07/DSC_0155edit.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/07/DSC_0155edit.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0182edit.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/DSC_0182edit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/DSC_0182edit.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/07/DSC_0182edit.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/07/DSC_0182edit.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0166edit.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/DSC_0166edit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/DSC_0166edit.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/07/DSC_0166edit.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/07/DSC_0166edit.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div></div></figure><p>Segundo, todos sabemos (y, si no, aquí se enteran <strong>😉</strong>) que en Puerto Rico los Tres Reyes Magos viajan en <strong>caballos</strong>, no camellos. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0222_Moment.jpg\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/DSC_0222_Moment.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/DSC_0222_Moment.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/07/DSC_0222_Moment.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0222_Moment.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0225_Moment.jpg\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/DSC_0225_Moment.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/DSC_0225_Moment.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/07/DSC_0225_Moment.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0225_Moment.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0232_Moment.jpg\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/DSC_0232_Moment.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/DSC_0232_Moment.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/07/DSC_0232_Moment.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0232_Moment.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0160edit.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1377\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/DSC_0160edit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/DSC_0160edit.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/07/DSC_0160edit.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/07/DSC_0160edit.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div></div></figure><p>Y tercero, los <strong>Reyes Magos</strong> de por sí están atados fuertemente a la cultura puertorriqueña. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0143edit-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/DSC_0143edit-1.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/DSC_0143edit-1.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/07/DSC_0143edit-1.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/DSC_0143edit-1.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h3 id=\"los-tres-reyes-magos-y-otros-personajes\">Los Tres Reyes Magos y otros personajes</h3><p>Como pueden haber notado, los reyes magos no fueron los únicos personajes que aparecieron en las carretas y carruajes de Cuco. En sus piezas también protagonizan San Valentín, la Virgen María, la Sagrada Familia y las \"Tres Marías\". </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/tempImageJl2Dnq.gif\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2845\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/tempImageJl2Dnq.gif 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/tempImageJl2Dnq.gif 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/07/tempImageJl2Dnq.gif 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/07/tempImageJl2Dnq.gif 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/07/tempImageFkjo2X.gif\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2835\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21